Category: D:Electricity, gas, steam and air conditioning supply/35:Electricity, gas, steam and air conditioning supply/351:Electric power generation, transmission and distribution/3510:Electric power generation, transmission and distribution
Description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/16277/documentation

This dataset is a market group. Market groups represent a 'market of markets'. Their purpose is to group a set of markets into larger, geographically relevant datasets.;Market groups are created for convenience and ease of use. They only group other markets and/or market groups contained within their geography.;Losses and relevant exchanges (transport, transport infrastructure, etc.) are not included in this dataset. They are present in the contained markets.  ;This is the market group for 'electricity, high voltage', in India.

This activity starts at the gate of markets that deliver 'electricity, high voltage', in geographies contained within the geography of this dataset.

This activity ends with the supply of 'electricity, high voltage',  to the consumers of this product within the geography of India.
